Ingevity Corporation Key Developments

Ingevity Corporation Presents at CJS Securities 17th Annual “New Ideas” Summer Conference, Jul-11-2017
Jul 7 17
Ingevity Corporation Presents at CJS Securities 17th Annual “New Ideas” Summer Conference, Jul-11-2017 . Venue: White Plains, New York, United States. Speakers: Dan Gallagher, vice president, investor relations, John C. Fortson, Chief Financial Officer, Executive Vice President and Treasurer, Michael Wilson, president and CEO.


Ingevity to Invest $20 Million for New Activated Carbon Extrusion Plant in Changshu, China
Jun 28 17
Ingevity Corporation announced that it will build a new activated carbon extrusion plant in Changshu, China representing an investment of approximately $20 million. The facility is expected to be operational by the fall of 2018.


Ingevity Corporation Presents at Houlihan Lokey 2017 Global Industrials Conference, May-18-2017 11:25 AM
May 12 17
Ingevity Corporation Presents at Houlihan Lokey 2017 Global Industrials Conference, May-18-2017 11:25 AM. Venue: Hilton Midtown New York, 1335 6th Avenue, New York NY, 10019, United States. Speakers: D. Michael Wilson, Chief Executive Officer, President and Director, Dan Gallagher, vice president, investor relations, John C. Fortson, Chief Financial Officer, Executive Vice President and Treasurer.


