Ingevity Corp.


            
            Ingevity Corp engages in the manufacture of specialty chemicals and carbon materials. It operates through the Performance Chemicals and Performance Materials segments. The Performance Materials segment consists of carbon technologies business which primarily produces automotive carbon products used in gasoline vapor emission control systems. The Performance Chemicals segment primarily addresses applications in three product families: pavement technologies, oilfield technologies, and industrial specialties. The company was founded on March 27, 2015 and is headquartered in North Charleston, SC.

            
            (See Full Profile)


  




