Careers | Ingevity - Ingevity

















 Menu




Careers at Ingevity








No challenge too big. No contribution too small.
Ingenuity and a relentless drive to solve complex problems have always been at the heart of everything we do. And it starts on the inside – with a team of talented, tenacious people pushing the bounds of what’s possible, every day.
We cultivate a workforce that reflects diversity in experience, skill, and perspective. We nurture both personal and professional development – at the workplace and in our communities.









Ready to achieve the improbable?
View Jobs







Salaried Benefits
Ingevity is committed to our employees’ careers and overall well-being. Because of this, we offer our U.S.-based employees a comprehensive benefits package from day one.
Vacation
Everyone needs time away from work. You’ll become eligible for three weeks of vacation after just three years of service. We also offer 13 paid holidays. The exact days off may vary at different locations to allow for operating needs and local flexibility.
401(k)
Ingevity will make an automatic fixed contribution of 3% of your pay to your 401(k) – even if you don’t contribute anything yourself! With the 6% company match, this means you could receive up to 9% of your annual pay in company contributions each year.
Health Insurance
We offer a choice of medical, dental and vision coverage. If you elect coverage, it's effective Day 1! We also offer a variety of other comprehensive benefits as a full time employee.
Wellness Rewards
You’ll have opportunities to improve your health and earn credit. By using a pedometer to track your activity, you could earn up to $500 in annual rewards. In addition to these great benefits, several Ingevity locations offer an onsite gym that employees can take advantage of.







Our Team
Ready to push the bounds of what’s possible to solve problems? So are we.
Learn More











Our people are empowered and engaged, free to drive innovation and productivity, explore processes and products, and develop and deliver solutions that make a real difference in the real world.
The things we do – enabling oil to flow better, colors to shine brighter, roads to last longer, and making the air we breathe cleaner – aren’t simple or easy. But we wouldn’t have it any other way. Because at Ingevity, we don’t just love a good challenge, we live for them.








