Ingevity Corp: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback
















ingevity corp
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Materials
Industry: Chemicals
Sub-Industry: Specialty Chemicals
Ingevity Corporation manufactures specialty chemicals. The Company offers adhesives, inks, soaps, detergents, agricultural chemicals, metalworking fluids, and lubricants. Ingevity markets its products worldwide.




